---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<PageLayout title="About — Clemente Lacerda" description="About Clemente Lacerda — background, beliefs, and principles.">
  <section class="about-page">
    <h1>About</h1>
    <div class="about-content">
      <p>
        I have been fortunate to grow up surrounded by people I love, and to keep meeting remarkable ones over time. I have two sisters and one brother, and I am the oldest. I am passionate about learning, building, and craft.<sup><a href="#fn-1" id="fnref-1" aria-describedby="footnotes-label">1</a></sup> I also believe that sharing the journey with people you admire, care for, and love makes any project and experience better.
      </p>
      <p>
        I was born and raised in Brazil. I lived in Singapore while completing my Master's in Finance at NUS Business School, and I am now based in New York as a first-year MBA student at Columbia. Singapore expanded my self-awareness, challenged old beliefs, and reshaped my worldview. New York reinforced how much a city can shape your inner life. Environment, context, and people matter.
      </p>
      <p>
        I believe that everything you do matters. Integrity is non-negotiable. There is no cheating reality. Compounding may be the closest thing we have to magic.<sup><a href="#fn-2" id="fnref-2" aria-describedby="footnotes-label">2</a></sup> Small actions, repeated consistently over long periods, create outsized outcomes.<sup><a href="#fn-3" id="fnref-3" aria-describedby="footnotes-label">3</a></sup>
      </p>
      <p>
        I keep a small set of principles and a long list of curiosities.
      </p>
    </div>
    <footer class="footnotes" aria-labelledby="footnotes-label">
      <h2 id="footnotes-label" class="visually-hidden">Footnotes</h2>
      <ol class="footnotes-list">
        <li id="fn-1">
          There is long-term satisfaction to be found not in attaining, but in becoming. Craftsmanship carries through a product and service — it has weight, it has meaning.
          <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8VHOO_WvOf4" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Inside Mizuno: Craft, Patience & Mastery</a>;
          <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=T7xYYJPs250" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Sho Kuwamoto on Figma's Product Craft</a>
        </li>
        <li id="fn-2">
          Often attributed to Albert Einstein: "Compound interest is the eighth wonder of the world."
        </li>
        <li id="fn-3">
          Popularized through "the butterfly effect," the idea that small changes can produce large consequences in complex systems.
        </li>
      </ol>
    </footer>
  </section>
</PageLayout>

<script>
  function initFootnoteScroll() {
    document.querySelectorAll<HTMLAnchorElement>('sup a[href^="#fn-"]').forEach((link) => {
      link.addEventListener('click', (e) => {
        e.preventDefault();
        const id = link.getAttribute('href')!.slice(1);
        const target = document.getElementById(id);
        if (target) {
          target.scrollIntoView({ behavior: 'smooth', block: 'nearest' });
        }
      });
    });
  }

  initFootnoteScroll();
  document.addEventListener('astro:after-swap', initFootnoteScroll);
</script>

<style>
  .about-page {
    padding-top: var(--space-3xl);
  }

  .about-page h1 {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2xl);
  }

  .about-content {
    max-width: var(--content-max-width);
  }

  .about-content p {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    line-height: var(--leading-body);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-body);
  }

  .about-content p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .about-content sup {
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    color: var(--color-accent);
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 0;
    vertical-align: super;
  }

  .about-content sup a {
    color: inherit;
    background-image: none;
  }

  .about-content sup a:hover {
    color: var(--color-text);
    background-size: 0% 0;
  }

  .about-content sup a:focus-visible {
    outline-offset: 1px;
  }

  .footnotes {
    max-width: var(--content-max-width);
    margin-top: var(--space-3xl);
    padding-top: var(--space-lg);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .footnotes-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding-left: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .footnotes-list li {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: var(--leading-body);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .footnotes-list li:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .footnotes-list li::before {
    content: counter(list-item) ". ";
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .footnotes a {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .footnotes a:hover {
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  @media (min-width: 640px) {
    .about-page {
      padding-top: var(--space-4xl);
    }
  }
</style>
